assist Italian companies and enterpreneurs to invest in Uganda as
well as to make joint ventures with Ugandan enterpreneurs.
</P>
<P>
Museveni told his guest that his government welcomes Italian
ivestors to Uganda, noting that the government puts a lot of emphasis
on investment promotion.
</P>
<P>
He said investment is a great stimulus to growth and the real
ignition for the transformation of the country.
</P>
<P>
