Ricoveri and his delegation included the Head of the Cooperation
Department, Counsellor Gianiuca Cortese, and the Head of the Economic
Department, Counsellor Gabriella Maneghello.
</P>
<P>
The meeting was attended by Ugandan Minister of State for Foreign
Affairs in charge of international affairs Martin Aliker. enditem

