welcome the return of Hong Kong to the motherland and the
convocation of the 15th National Party Congress
</P>
<P>
Wei Jianxing, a member of the Political Bureau of the CPC
Central Committee and chairman of the All-China Federation of
Trade Unions, made a lengthy speech at the meeting. He called on
all workers to learn more about the socialist market economy and
have confidence in the reform of state-owned enterprises, and help
laid-off workers find new job opportunities.
</P>
<P>
In another development, Hu Jintao also met with a delegation of
Hong Kong Federation of Trade Unions and May Day tour members from
trade unions of Hong Kong and Macao.  
