political issues" the Agreement on Mutual Reduction of Military
Forces in Border Areas between China and the four countries,
Russia, Kazakhstan, Kyrgyzstan and Tajikistan.
</P>
<P>
For the first time, the five nations of the Asia-Pacific region
have solved a series of sensative problems through peaceful
negotiations, he said.
</P>
<P>
Jiang made the visit from April 22 to April 26 which resulted
in the two documents. During his stay, Jiang also spoke to the
Russian State Duma, the lower house of the Russian parliament.
