<HEADLINE> Turkey, Romania Sign 3 Accords </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ANKARA, April 29 (Xinhua) -- Turkey and Romania today signed a
free trade agreement and two accords on cooperation in the fields
of animal health and plant protection.
</P>
<P>
The agreements were inked here following official talks
between Turkish President Suleyman Demirel and his Romanian
