rare animals of 24 species, including snub-nosed monkeys, addaxes,
blue sheep, red deers, and wild donkeys, since it started
artificial breeding work four years ago.
</P>
<P>
The wild donkey, spotted leopard, lynx, lesser panda, and blue
deer will probably have babies this year, according to zoo
officials. 
